12:12.351 --> 12:13.545
S-19?

12:27.166 --> 12:28.963
<i>Seven</i>

12:29.601 --> 12:33.560
<i>That's the time we leave,</i>
<i>at seven</i>

12:34.873 --> 12:38.809
<i>I'll be waitin' up</i>
<i>for heaven</i>

12:39.878 --> 12:44.508
<i>Countin' every mile</i>
<i>of railroad track</i>

12:44.583 --> 12:47.711
<i>That takes me back</i>

12:48.487 --> 12:52.981
<i>Never thought my heart</i>
<i>could be so yearny</i>

12:53.792 --> 12:57.455
<i>Why did I decide to roam?</i>

12:58.997 --> 13:03.525
<i>Wanna make</i>
<i>a sentimental journey</i>

13:04.069 --> 13:08.130
<i>Sentimental journey home</i>

13:10.175 --> 13:12.166
That was fun, great fun!

13:12.244 --> 13:15.577
Let us have
some more longnecks,
some more tunes.

13:15.647 --> 13:17.911
Francois, now,
don't you think...

13:18.617 --> 13:19.982
Oh, sorry.

13:20.752 --> 13:23.312
Don't you think
that maybe we should
mingle a little bit?

13:23.388 --> 13:25.856
I mean, now that
we're kind of known
around here,

13:25.924 --> 13:28.324
we could start
asking a few questions,

13:28.393 --> 13:30.691
like...
Who the hell
are you guys?

13:31.363 --> 13:34.423
We are, uh,
just simple sailors

13:34.499 --> 13:36.364
having an evening
on top of the town.

13:36.435 --> 13:39.233
But of course.
Cops?

13:39.471 --> 13:41.530
No, we're not cops.

13:41.607 --> 13:44.576
Well, you sure
don't look like
simple sailors, either.

13:45.544 --> 13:47.171
Alcoholic Beverage Control?

13:47.246 --> 13:49.908
Oh, look...

13:50.883 --> 13:52.145
Tiffany.

13:52.217 --> 13:56.176
Tiffany, I mean, we're just
here having a couple of beers,
minding our own business,

13:56.255 --> 13:58.086
waiting for a friend of ours
to show up.

13:58.156 --> 14:01.819
Yes, a very good friend.
The Pearl.
Perhaps you know him?

14:03.462 --> 14:04.929
You wanna see Pearl?

14:04.997 --> 14:06.521
He's expecting us.

14:11.236 --> 14:12.965
You guys wait right here.

14:14.106 --> 14:17.166
This is very easy.
She knows The Pearl.

14:18.110 --> 14:19.304
Maybe.

14:19.378 --> 14:22.472
Either that, or she thinks
we're a couple of gangsters
or something.

14:22.547 --> 14:23.980
Don't be ridiculous.

14:24.049 --> 14:26.176
Francois, please,
when we're in
a place like this,

14:26.251 --> 14:28.583
let me do the talking.
Why?

14:28.654 --> 14:30.918
Why? Be...

14:31.390 --> 14:34.689
I'm sorry, but you
don't exactly fit in.

14:34.760 --> 14:36.352
Now, we're not gonna
get the results we'd like.

14:36.428 --> 14:38.020
Come with me.

14:38.497 --> 14:42.797
The Pearl?
A very good friend of his.
Come on.

14:46.838 --> 14:47.964
Uh-uh.

14:48.273 --> 14:52.232
The Pearl's friend
is really shy.

14:52.311 --> 14:54.541
But...
You stay here.

14:54.846 --> 14:57.007
You sing.
What?

14:57.082 --> 14:58.879
Or no Pearl.

